high_descs: Turn left and walk forward to face the counter to the right of the fridge.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Look down to face the lettuce on the counter.
Cut the lettuce on the counter into slices.
Turn around and step forward to face the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn around and step forward to face the lettuce on the counter.
Pick up the slice of lettuce on the counter.
Turn around and step forward to face the sink.
Wash the lettuce slice in the sink and then remove it.
Walk around the right side of the center table to face the trash can.
Place the lettuce slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To wash a slice of lettuce and place it in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn around, go pass the fridge and turn left to face the toaster.
Pick up the knife to the right of the toaster.
Look down at the lettuce on the counter.
Cut the lettuce on the counter.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn around and go back to the counter with the toaster.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Turn around and go back to the sink.
Rinse the lettuce in the sink and pick it up.
Turn right, go to the end of the counter and turn left to go to the trash can.
Put the lettuce in the trash can behind the right bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed slice of lettuce in the trash.

high_descs: Go to the toaster
Pick up the knife next to the toaster
Look down at the lettuce
Cut the lettuce
Go to the sink
Put the knife in the sink
Go to the cut lettuce
Pick up a slice of lettuce
Go to the sink
Wash the lettuce
Go to the black bin
Put the lettuce in the black bin
anns.task_desc: Put a washed slice of lettuce in a bin
